  <div class="border border-gray-200 px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-7xl" data-tabs-target="tab" id="tab-bungarribee">
      <h1 class="text-pretty text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950 data-[dark]:text-white sm:text-6xl">Bungarribee Park</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-medium text-gray-600">Western Sydney Parklands</p>
      <div>
        <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">19 January</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">20 April</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">20 July</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">19 October</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="mt-8 lg:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-12">
        <div class="max-w-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="course-start-bungarribee">Course Start Point</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">The course starts adjacent to the Bung Shelter, near the main carpark for Bungarribee Park and the Warrigal dog run. This is the same starting point as Rooty Hill parkrun. Vehicle access to Bungarribee Park is at the intersection of Doonside Road and Holbeche Road.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Arrive at 6:45am for a 7am race start.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text-lg/6 text-gray-600"><a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/uRW59Ysg1rT4FTw66">Google Maps Link</a> | <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://maps.apple.com/?address=Bungarribee%20NSW%202767,%20Australia&auid=2305727777122935073&ll=-33.783882,150.868367&lsp=9902&q=Rooty%20Hill%20Parkrun&t=m">Apple Maps Link</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:row-span-2 mt-8 lg:my-auto">
          <%= image_tag "bungarribee-start.png", class: "rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-lg mt-8 lg:col-span-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="facilities-bungarribee">Facilities</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">There is plenty of car parking and places to secure a bike (bring your own lock).</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text/6 text-gray-600">There are public toilet facilities 200m from the course start and a drinking fountain (with dog bowl below) at the course start.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mt-8 lg:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-12">
        <div class="max-w-lg lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="course-description-bungarribee">Course Description</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">The course is mostly on sealed (concrete/bitumen) tracks but there are two gravel sections and a dirt section that can be muddy after rain. The course is a large, looping out and back course and you're never more than about 1.5km from the start point.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg/6 text-gray-600"><a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3336193874389944524">Strava Route</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:row-span-2 mt-8 lg:my-auto lg:order-1">
          <div class="strava-embed-placeholder" data-embed-type="route" data-embed-id="3336193874389944524" data-units="metric" data-full-width="true" data-style="standard" data-surface-type="true" data-map-hash="12.89/-33.78104/150.86593" data-club-id="1343589" data-from-embed="true"></div><script src="https://strava-embeds.com/embed.js"></script>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-lg lg:order-3">
          <h2 class="mt-9 lg:mt-0 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="event-rego-bungarribee">Event Registration</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">To participate, you just need to be registered on this site. If you've run or signed up before, you're all set. Use the <%= link_to "forgot password form", forgot_password_path, class: "text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> to reset your password or set it for the first time.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">To register as a WS10 runner, fill in the <%= link_to "registration form", sign_up_path, class: "text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> and then click on the confirmation link in your email.</p>
          <% if false %>
            <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Tell us your coming (and help spread the word!) by indicating you will come to the <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="<%= @next_bungarribee_event_strava %>">Strava Event</a> or the <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="<%= @next_bungarribee_event_fb %>">Facebook Event</a>.</p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div data-tabs-target="tab" id="tab-nepean" hidden>
      <h1 class="text-pretty text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950 data-[dark]:text-white sm:text-6xl">Nepean River</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-medium text-gray-600">Tench Reserve, Jamisontown</p>
