            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">16 February</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">18 May</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">17 August</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">16 November</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="max-w-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="course-start-nepean">Course Start Point</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">The course starts and finishes in Tench Reserve, in the same general area as Nepean River parkrun. If driving, there is parking on Tench Avenue and in carparks off Tench avenue.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Arrive at 6:45am for a 7am race start.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text-lg/6 text-gray-600"><a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Nepean+River+Parkrun/@-33.7623863,150.6611338,17z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x6b1289ec090c8baf:0xa9d1ffa8acefca12!8m2!3d-33.7623908!4d150.6637087!16s%2Fg%2F11t9c9zkpm!5m1!1e1?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDEyNi4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D">Google Maps Link</a> | <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://maps.apple.com/?address=163%E2%80%93165%20Tench%20Ave%0APenrith%20NSW%202750%0AAustralia&auid=1916632410848447481&ll=-33.762531,150.663880&lsp=9902&q=Nepean%20River%20Parkrun&t=m">Apple Maps Link</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:row-span-2 mt-8 lg:my-auto">
          <%= image_tag "nepean-start.png", class: "rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
        <div class="max-lg:mt-8 lg:col-span-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="facilities-nepean">Facilities</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">There is plenty of car parking and places to secure a bike (bring your own lock).</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text/6 text-gray-600">There are multiple public toilet facilities, both at the start/finish line and on the course but they may not open until the event has commenced. Multiple drinking fountains are available too.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="max-w-lg lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="course-description-nepean">Course Description</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">The event is run entirely on sealed cycle/pedestrian paths that are well suited to pushing a pram and resistant to adverse weather. The course is an out and back course around the river. There are no road crossings but expect to encounter lots of runners and walkers along with some cyclists.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg/6 text-gray-600"><a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3349254877669215002">Strava Route</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:row-span-2 mt-8 lg:my-auto lg:order-1">
          <div class="strava-embed-placeholder" data-embed-type="route" data-embed-id="3349254877669215002" data-units="metric" data-full-width="true" data-style="standard" data-surface-type="true" data-map-hash="12.66/-33.75417/150.67187" data-club-id="1343589" data-from-embed="true"></div><script src="https://strava-embeds.com/embed.js"></script>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-lg lg:order-3">
          <h2 class="mt-9 lg:mt-0 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="event-rego-nepean">Event Registration</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">To participate, you just need to be registered on this site. If you've run or signed up before, you're all set. Use the <%= link_to "forgot password form", forgot_password_path, class: "text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> to reset your password or set it for the first time.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">To register as a new WS10 runner, fill in the <%= link_to "registration form", sign_up_path, class: "text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> and then click on the confirmation link in your email.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Once you're registered, tell us your coming to this particular event (and help spread the word!) by RSVPing to the <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="<%= @next_nepean_event_strava %>">Strava Event</a> or the <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="<%= @next_nepean_event_fb %>">Facebook Event</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div data-tabs-target="tab" id="tab-parramatta" hidden>
      <h1 class="text-pretty text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-gray-950 data-[dark]:text-white sm:text-6xl">Parramatta</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-2xl font-medium text-gray-600">Parramatta Park</p>
      <div>
        <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">16 March</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">15 June</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-500 line-through">21 September</div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white px-4 py-5 shadow-sm sm:p-6">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16">
              <div class="bg-primary absolute transform rotate-45 text-center text-white font-semibold py-1 right-[-60px] top-[20px] w-[190px]">
                Next Event
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary">21 December</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="max-w-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="course-start-parramatta">Course Start Point</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Meet at the course finish point, near the Lady Fitzroy Memorial, just inside the old Tudorhouse Gates at George Street. After the pre-event briefing we'll move as a group to the start point near the Noller Footbridge.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Arrive at 6:45am for a 7am race start.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text-lg/6 text-gray-600"><a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Lady+Fitzroy+Memorial/@-33.8125395,150.9986062,19z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x6b12a33ae9a94bd1:0x4911e09a6c662c92!8m2!3d-33.8125742!4d150.9996972!16s%2Fg%2F11gwg61mh_!5m1!1e1?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDEyNi4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D">Google Maps Link</a> | <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://maps.apple.com/?address=O'Connell%20St,%20Parramatta%20NSW%202150,%20Australia&auid=755998292114138734&ll=-33.812575,150.999681&lsp=9902&q=Lady%20Mary%20Fitzroy&t=m">Apple Maps Link</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:row-span-2 mt-8 lg:my-auto">
          <%= image_tag "parramatta-start-map.png", class: "rounded-lg mb-2" %>
          <%= image_tag "parramatta-start-photo.jpg", class: "rounded-lg mt-2" %>
        </div>
        <div class="max-lg:mt-8 lg:col-span-1">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="facilities-parramatta">Facilities</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">There is usually plenty of parking within Parramatta Park and along the park road. Additional parking may also be available in the council car park in O’Connell Street next to CommBank (Parramatta) Stadium. It is a short walk from the O’Connell Street car park to the meeting point via the Noller footbridge.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 text/6 text-gray-600">There are public toilet facilities, both at the start/finish line and on the course. Multiple drinking fountains are available around the course too.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="max-w-lg lg:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="course-description-parramatta">Course Description</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">The event is run entirely on sealed cycle/pedestrian paths that are well suited to pushing a pram and resistant to adverse weather. The course consists of three (and a bit) laps of the park loop, starting near the Noller Footbridge and finishing in front of the George Street gatehouse.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg/6 text-gray-600"><a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3332104237298943424">Strava Route</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:row-span-2 mt-8 lg:my-auto lg:order-1">
          <div class="strava-embed-placeholder" data-embed-type="route" data-embed-id="3332104237298943424" data-units="metric" data-full-width="true" data-style="standard" data-surface-type="true" data-map-hash="12.89/-33.78104/150.86593" data-club-id="1343589" data-from-embed="true"></div><script src="https://strava-embeds.com/embed.js"></script>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-lg lg:order-3">
          <h2 class="mt-9 lg:mt-0 text-2xl font-medium tracking-tight" id="event-rego-parramatta">Event Registration</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">To participate, you just need to be registered on this site. If you've run or signed up before, you're all set. Use the <%= link_to "forgot password form", forgot_password_path, class: "text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> to reset your password or set it for the first time.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">To register as a new WS10 runner, fill in the <%= link_to "registration form", sign_up_path, class: "text-brand-brown hover:text-brand-grey underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline" %> and then click on the confirmation link in your email.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text/6 text-gray-600">Tell us your coming (and help spread the word!) by indicating you will come to the <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="<%= @next_parramatta_event_strava %>">Strava Event</a> or the <a class="text-brand-brown underline underline-offset-3 hover:no-underline hover:text-brand-grey" href="<%= @next_parramatta_event_fb %>">Facebook Event</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
